    Ventura comprises of two stages- 

<h3 class="style11"><u style="Color:white">STAGE 1 :</u></h3>
    <p style="Color:white; " class="style10"> Design a strategy for a product which is to be launched in the market taking into accounts the pros and cons, in accordance with the rules. The product must be one of the provided problem statements.</p> 
<ul style="Color:white ; font-size: 17px;">

 <li><a href="PDF/Fitbit.pdf" target="_blank"> <u Style="color:white">FitBit </u></a></li>
 <li><a href="PDF/wifi.pdf" target="_blank"> <u Style="color:white">WifiPen</u></a></li>
 <li><a href="PDF/Indcook.pdf" target="_blank"> <u Style="color:white">Induction Cooker</u></a> </li>
</ul>
<h3 style="Color:white" class="style11"> <u>STAGE 2 : </u></h3> 
<p style="Color:white ; font-size: 17px;"><strong>This stage has two parts-:</strong>
	       In the first part participating teams have to make a poster which will appeal from the 
           consumer regarding their product and must contain the basic features of the product.
	       The next part is a presentation on the product in which the participating team have 
           to describe their marketing strategy regarding the product and the stategy should be 
           well drafted keeping in view the products advantages, disadvantages, consumer group etc.
</p>
<h3 style="Color:white"> <u><span class="style11">RULES :</span></u><span 
        class="style11"> </span> </h3>
 <ul style="Color:white ; font-size: 17px;">
<li> One team may comprise of max. 3 members</li>
 
<li>One contestant can be a part of more than one team. But, you will have to register separately for each entry. </li> 

<li>A team can choose only one product out of three provided for the first stage. </li>

<li>Strategy for stage 1 must contain the following in sequential order: 
<ul>
	<li>Logo</li>
	<li>Punch line</li>
	<li>Product Description</li>
	<li>Differentiation</li>
	<li>Price Point</li>
	<li>Marketing Strategy</li>
	<li>Demerit Handling</li>
	<li>Cost Justification</li>
	<li>Investment approximation for publicity etc.</li> 
</ul> </li>
<li>Font size:14,12 (14 for titles and 12 for rest)</li> 

 <li>Teams for stage 2 will be shortlisted on the basis of stage 1 abstract.</li> 
 <li>Strategies for first stage should be given before October 15, 2011</li>

 <li>The summaries must be sent to <b>ventura@techsrijan.com </b>in pdf format. </li>

<li>Entries submitted after the deadlines shall not be considered. </li>
</ul>
<p style="Color:white ; font-size: 17px;">
Entries for stage 1 should be to the point as per the rules. Superfluous language is to be avoided. <em>Competition is open for students from non-technical fields as well.</em> </p>


